Miyaanay arkayn inaanu yeellay Xaram Aamin ah, halka dadka laga dafo hareerahooda13? Ee ma waxaan jirin oo been ah bay weli rumeysan yihiin, oo ku gaaloobaan Nicmadda Ilaahay?
